serverConfig.help:
**Server configuration manual** WiP

``help`` - Displays help for ``serverConfig``
``!mi joinMessage "Welcome to %u on the server"`` - Sets custom welcome messsage
``!mi serverConfig leaveMessage "Bye, %u :("`` - Sets custom farewell messsage
``!mi serverConfig joinMessageTest`` - Sends the current welcome message
``!mi serverConfig leaveMessageTest`` - Sends the current farewell message
serverConfig.joinMessageHelp: Example of use: ``!mi serverConfig joinMessage "Welcome to %u on the server"``
serverConfig.joinMessageError:
This isn't how you use this command
Example: ``!mi serverConfig joinMessage "Welcome to %u on the server"``
serverConfig.joinMessageMissUser: Warning! Your message doesn't contain a user nick, you can fix it by adding ``%u`` in the message
serverConfig.leaveMessageError:
This isn't how you use this command
Example: ``!mi serverConfig leaveMessage "Bye, %u :("``
serverConfig.leaveMessageMissUser: Warning! Your message doesn't contain a user nick, you can fix it by adding ``%u`` to the message
serverConfig.leaveMessageNull: This server doesn't have a custom welcome message set
